Specification of Updates:
1.	Visual Overhaul: I am replacing the isometric house with a 3D technical schematic that matches your reference image exactly, including the specific placement of the Sun, Solar Panels, Inverter, Meter, and Power Grid.
2.	Color-Coded Electrical Flows:
o DC (Direct Current): Solid/Animated Orange lines from panels to the Inverter.
o AC (Alternating Current): Solid/Animated Blue lines from the Inverter to the Meter and into the house loads.
3.	Dynamic Labels (A-F):
o A: TNB Bill (RM) input.
o B: Estimated Monthly Usage (kWh).
o C: Solar Generation (kWh).
o D: Morning Usage offset (kWh).
o E: Energy Exported to Grid (kWh).
o F: Energy Imported from Grid (kWh).
Only need above information. Others information no need showed in apps. Like the photo attached. Follow photo attached to generate the TECHNICAL SCHEMATIC
